description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: My Cat Just Reincarnated As My Dog Edition ! 

It was a wild and wacky week in the world of the Paranormal!  Tim and Bruiser bring you the headlines including plenty of UFO and shadow people encounters from around the globe! A woman is convinced her cat has just reincarnated as her dog, You are more likely to get bit by a Shark during a full moon and don't you just hate it when you get Pebbles in your Mars rover?
